<A>__{the threesome step from the car, keep close to a wall. schreber alone steps up to the door, leans down to a mat at the foot of the door, lifts it and takes a key from underneath. he unlocks the door, opens it, puts the key back, goes inside. he waves the other men forward. white and bumstead step up to the door bumstead looks at the mat it says: welcome on it.}
